Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.04,Captions,,0,0,0,,If AI is going to\Nrevolutionize healthcare...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:05.96,Captions,,0,0,0,,...who does it for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.82,Captions,,0,0,0,,Because they can barely\Nkeep the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.68,Captions,,0,0,0,,So let's do it for them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:12.78,Captions,,0,0,0,,What if we provided healthcare AI\Nas a service?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.14,Captions,,0,0,0,,We find all of those cancers.\NWe bring them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.06,Captions,,0,0,0,,All of your A1Cs greater than nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.06,Captions,,0,0,0,,...who haven't followed up\Nwith their primary care doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:21.26,Captions,,0,0,0,,...in a year, two years -\Nbring them back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.86,Captions,,0,0,0,,All of that health data exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.36,Captions,,0,0,0,,...on your health\Ninformation exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.62,Captions,,0,0,0,,What if we build\Nan intelligence layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.00,Captions,,0,0,0,,...that sat over the top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:30.24,Captions,,0,0,0,,...constantly crawling\Nthrough that data...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:33.12,Captions,,0,0,0,,...looking for signals,\Nlooking for ways to make you better?
